16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1151.15, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 1151.15. A. The Roofing Hearing Board is authorized to
19 investigate any written complaint received pursuant to the Roofing
20 Contractor Registration Act, including any person to the extent
