17 the nature of process the complaint as provided by law. The
18 registrar shall notify the roofing contractor against whom the
19 complaint is made, in writing, within five (5) days of the receipt
20 of the written complaint. The roofing contractor shall have ten
21 (10) days to respond, in writing, to the registrar. If a response
22 to the complaint is received by the registrar, whether admitting or
23 denying the basis of the complaint, a copy of both the complaint and
24 the response shall be sent to the district attorney along with the
