19 the court orders the registration suspended, revoked or denied, and
20 yet fails to set the term of such suspension, revocation or denial,
21 the period shall be six (6) months.
22 F. The registrar shall not renew, reinstate, or issue a new
23 roofing contractor registration to any person subject to any term of
24 denial, suspension or revocation until such term has been completed,
