15 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1151.18, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1151.18. Upon request, the registrar shall verify a
18 roofing contractor registration number to city, county and state
19 enforcement officials and to the public. The registrar shall
20 establish through the Internet or other technology a verification
21 system or direct access system for confirming roofing contractor
22 registration certificates and status of registration maintained by
23 the Construction Industries Board. The system shall include the
24 notation of each complaint received against an individual roofing
